<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Winter Puffer Jacket</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f5f5f5;
color:#111;
}

.container{
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
padding:50px 20px;
}

.product{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:50px;
align-items:center;
}

.product-image{
flex:1;
min-width:300px;
}

.product-image img{
width:100%;
border-radius:20px;
background:white;
padding:20px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.product-info{
flex:1;
min-width:300px;
}

.brand{
color:#c70000;
font-weight:bold;
letter-spacing:2px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

h1{
font-size:48px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.price{
font-size:36px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#c70000;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.description{
line-height:1.8;
margin-bottom:25px;
color:#555;
}

label{
display:block;
margin-bottom:8px;
font-weight:bold;
}

select,input{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin-bottom:20px;
border:1px solid #ddd;
border-radius:8px;
}

button{
width:100%;
padding:16px;
background:#c70000;
color:white;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
font-size:18px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
background:#900000;
}

.features{
margin-top:40px;
}

.features li{
margin-bottom:10px;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:40px;
margin-top:50px;
background:#111;
color:white;
}

@media(max-width:768px){
h1{
font-size:34px;
}

.product{
flex-direction:column;
}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="product">

<div class="product-image">
<img src="jacket.png" alt="Winter Jacket">
</div>

<div class="product-info">

<div class="brand">THREADHEAVEN</div>

<h1>Premium Winter Puffer Jacket</h1>

<div class="price">Rs. 7,999</div>

<p class="description">
Stay warm and stylish this winter with our premium insulated puffer jacket.
Designed with a luxurious fur-lined hood, durable outer shell, and modern fit,
this jacket is perfect for cold-weather adventures and everyday wear.
</p>

<label>Choose Size</label>
<select>
<option>S</option>
<option>M</option>
<option>L</option>
<option>XL</option>
<option>XXL</option>
</select>

<label>Quantity</label>
<input type="number" value="1" min="1">

<button>Add To Cart</button>

<div class="features">
<ul>
<li>✓ Water Resistant Fabric</li>
<li>✓ Fur Lined Hood</li>
<li>✓ Premium Insulation</li>
<li>✓ Winter Collection 2026</li>
<li>✓ Free Delivery Across Pakistan</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<footer>
© 2026 THREADHEAVEN — Premium Winter Collection
</footer>

</body>
</html>
